Class SimuContextImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.BasicNotifierImpl
      • org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.BasicEObjectImpl
        • org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, NameTag, SimuContext, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class SimuContextImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements SimuContext
    An implementation of the model object 'Network'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Net Type
    • Resource Type
    • Msg Hub
    • Aclf Net
    • Acsc Net
    • DStability Net
    • Dist Net
    • Dc Sys Net
    • Opf Net
    • Loadflow Algorithm
    • Simple Fault Algorithm
    • Dyn Simu Algorithm
    • Dclf Algorithm
